 126:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 3: rich power-chord bass with mixed waveforms + huge filter sweep ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 127:src/voice.h   **** //   Mixed shapes for body: saw root (harmonic-rich), square fifth (hollow), a
 128:src/voice.h   **** //   clean sine sub (tight low end), saw octave on top. Starts dark, then
