 165:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 5: screaming aggressive lead ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 166:src/voice.h   **** //   Detuned sawtooth stack (root + a hair-sharp twin + octave) for a thick,
 167:src/voice.h   **** //   buzzing supersaw bite, pushed up into a cutting register. Heavy drive and a
